            "title": "Tuscany, May 2024",
            "rating": "5",
            "avatar": "/uploads/images/portfolio-06.webp"
          }
        },
        "t-3": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "The calm on the day was the gift. Every vendor had talked to them, every detail was handled, and the two of us got to be actual guests at our own wedding.",
            "name": "Mei & Arjun",
            "title": "Windham Peak, September 2024",
            "rating": "5"
          }
        },
        "t-4": {
          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote": "They said no to a few things we loved, and were right about every one of them. We'd hand them another wedding tomorrow.",
